ia N. Mochegova</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140531203033872"><h3 class="no_margin">Michele S. Swanson</h3><p>  <sup>4</sup>  Department of Microbiology and Immunology, University of Michigan Medical School, Ann Arbor, Michigan, United States of America,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Swanson%20MS%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20062534">Michele S. Swanson</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140531203031504"><h3 class="no_margin">Zijiang Zhao</h3><p>  <sup>5</sup>  Department of Pathology and Immunology, Washington University School of Medicine, St. Louis, Missouri, United States of America,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Zhao%20Z%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20062534">Zijiang Zhao</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140531200730896"><h3 class="no_margin">Herbert W. Virgin</h3><p>  <sup>5</sup>  Department of Pathology and Immunology, Washington University School of Medicine, St. Louis, Missouri, United States of America,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Virgin%20HW%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20062534">Herbert W. Virgin</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140531200728528"><h3 class="no_margin">Daniel Portnoy</h3><p>  <sup>1</sup>  Department of Molecular and Cellular Biology, University of California, Berkeley, California, United States of America,   </p><p>  <sup>3</sup>  School of Public Health, University of California, Berkeley, California, United States of America,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Portnoy%20D%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20062534">Daniel Portnoy</a></div></div></div></div><div class="contrib-group half_rhythm fm-editor">Adam J. Ratner, <span class="fm-role">Editor</span><sup></sup></div><div class="fm-panel half_rhythm"><div class="togglers"><a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm140531197674496_ai idm140531205191936_ai idm140531198721568_ai">Author information</a> <a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm140531197674496_an